OL,3,CParents sue hospital that 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' before death of little
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,FThe parents of a three-year-old girl
OL,8,Fwho died after doctors "missed
OL,9,Fopportunities" to diagnose a rare
OL,10,Fcondition have vowed to sue the
OL,11,Fhospital where she was treated.
OL,13,FRyleigh Hillcoat-Bee was admitted to
OL,14,FBlackpool Victoria Hospital in August
OL,15,F2021 after she became floppy and
OL,16,Flethargic following a family trip to
OL,17,FNorth Wales.
