OL,3,CParents sue hospital that 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' before death of little
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,FDoctors discovered she had elevated
OL,8,Flevels of potassium in her blood as
OL,9,Fwell as a high heart rate and
OL,10,Fbreathing rate.
OL,12,FBut, at an inquest into her death
OL,13,FCoroner Alan Wilson said medical
OL,14,Fprofessionals had missed opportunities
OL,15,Fto scrutinise the "red flag" symptoms
OL,16,Fbefore discharging her after five days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
