OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,FThree months later, and still waiting
OL,8,Ffor follow-up tests, she was admitted
OL,9,Fto hospital after becoming unwell
OL,10,Fagain.
OL,12,FShe died on 8 November 2021 following
OL,13,Fa cardiac arrest.
OL,15,FAn inquest at Blackpool Coroner's
OL,16,FCourt ruled that there had been
OL,17,Fseveral "missed opportunities" in her
OL,18,Fcare.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
