OL,7,FRyleigh's parents Andrew Hillcoat and
OL,8,FCaroline Bee said: "We are very upset
OL,9,Fat the loss of our little girl.
OL,11,F"We had to fight for a full inquest
OL,12,Finto her death and it has been a long
OL,13,Fand traumatising journey.
OL,15,F"We are devastated about the coroner's
OL,16,Ffinding despite robust evidence that
OL,17,FRyleigh's rhabdomyolysis flare up in
OL,18,FAugust 2021 could and should have been
OL,19,Feffectively managed.
OL,26,@pD@TOU
