OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,F"We believe that Ryleigh should still
OL,8,Fbe here today, but she was not given
OL,9,Fany chance of survival."
OL,11,FRepresenting the parents, Diane
OL,12,FRostron, a medical negligence
OL,13,Fsolicitor, said: "The hospital was
OL,14,Fgiven clear advice from colleagues in
OL,15,FLeeds during Ryleigh's admission in
OL,16,FAugust 2021 to seek specialist advice
OL,17,Ffrom a neuromuscular specialist.
OL,19,F"Had they done so, identifying
OL,20,Frhabdomyolysis, and advice on how to
OL,21,Ftreat a flare up, would have followed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@XO]uD@ROU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
