OL,3,CParents sue hospital that 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' before death of little
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,F"The hospital would and should have
OL,8,Fthen provided this information to
OL,9,FRyleigh's parents while the root cause
OL,10,Fof Ryleigh's condition was being
OL,11,Finvestigated.
OL,13,F"Ryleigh died on 8th November 2021
OL,14,Fjust three months after being
OL,15,Fdischarged at the very hospital where
OL,16,Fshe was born a little over three years
OL,17,Fearlier.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
