OL,3,CParents sue hospital that 'missed
OL,4,Copportunities' before death of little
OL,5,Cgirl
OL,7,F"Instead of being advised that Ryleigh
OL,8,Fwas suffering from rhabdomyolysis and
OL,9,Fproviding her parents with guidance on
OL,10,Fhow to manage this safely, my clients
OL,11,Fwere instead told that Ryleigh would
OL,12,Frecover as quickly as she became
OL,13,Funwell.
OL,15,F"We believe that Ryleigh's death could
OL,16,Fhave been prevented and have been
OL,17,Finstructed to pursue a medical
OL,18,Fnegligence claim."
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@RO]
