OL,7,FChris Barben, Executive Medical
OL,8,FDirector at Blackpool Teaching
OL,9,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust, said:
OL,10,F"I would first of all like to offer
OL,11,Fsincere condolences to Ryleigh's
OL,12,Ffamily and everyone touched by her
OL,13,Flife personally and on behalf of
OL,14,Feveryone at the Trust.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
