OL,7,F"While we know this cannot bring
OL,8,FRyleigh back, we will be carefully
OL,9,Fconsidering the Coroner's findings
OL,10,Faround the way the Trust conducted
OL,11,Fitself during this tragic incident to
OL,12,Fensure that we learn everything we can
OL,13,Ffrom what happened and work to prevent
OL,14,Fanything like it happening again."
